http://www.thehindu.com/news/cities/Kochi/Support-for-coconut-based-units/article13989254.ece

Coconut Development Board will provide technical and financial support for establishment of coconut-based industries.An official release said that financial support will be extended to the tune of 25 per cent of the project cost limited to Rs. 50 lakh. Entrepreneurs could avail the benefits for setting up coconut based industries. Coconut producer companies / coconut producer federations could submit project proposals for establishing value added products from neera including cookies, chocolate, sugar and other related products under the scheme. More details may be had from 0484-2376265.